  "detailed_description": "<h1>Upcoming Update Plans</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/5ddc936aa111697858636e9de4243b69.avif?t=1773392771\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras_big/5ddc936aa111697858636e9de4243b69.avif?t=1773392771 width=800 height=1540 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Introduction：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Coin Push RPG is a casual idle game incorporating coin-pusher mechanics, featuring abundant content and multiple gameplay modes. The game includes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1:1 Replicated Coin-Pusher Simulator Mode</strong> - Faithfully recreates the arcade coin-pusher experience</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adventure Mode</strong> - Complete with extensive character backgrounds, talent combinations, and equipment selection</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenge Mode</strong> - Combines fast-paced monster battles with idle mechanisms for effortless farming</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will recruit heroes, customize their unique talent skills, assemble various team formations, and lead them on treasure-hunting expeditions. Upgrade your village, craft legendary equipment, and enhance your strength to conquer the Demon King!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/0c250afed965c08fb8d302e1c0a4b7e3.poster.avif?t=1773392771\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/0c250afed965c08fb8d302e1c0a4b7e3.webm?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/0c250afed965c08fb8d302e1c0a4b7e3.mp4?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Coin Push Mode – 1:1 Replica</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game, players can experience an <strong>authentic 1:1 replica of a real coin pusher arcade machine</strong>, featuring:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rotating Wheel (Lucky Spin)</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tower Stacker (Tower Bonus)</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>JP123 Jackpot</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Full-Table Grand Prize</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/bc3f8517f8979228b3251249bb2af113.poster.avif?t=1773392771\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/bc3f8517f8979228b3251249bb2af113.webm?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/bc3f8517f8979228b3251249bb2af113.mp4?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/02bc8e7d9fb022fd5b5a3359268a9a8b.poster.avif?t=1773392771\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/02bc8e7d9fb022fd5b5a3359268a9a8b.webm?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/02bc8e7d9fb022fd5b5a3359268a9a8b.mp4?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Idle Coin Pushing – Relaxing Auto-Battler</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During battles, the coins collected from the <strong>Coin Pusher</strong> will be distributed to your heroes. They’ll only fight for you once they get their fair share!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pay up</strong> to make your heroes work for you—or just <strong>sit back, auto-drop coins</strong>, and let them grind for you effortlessly! <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/1c7aaeb6cbe5654783f02569796e45fb.poster.avif?t=1773392771\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/1c7aaeb6cbe5654783f02569796e45fb.webm?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/1c7aaeb6cbe5654783f02569796e45fb.mp4?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hero Recruitment & Character Development</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every hero comes with <strong>unique backstories and rarity tiers</strong>. Recruit and train a diverse team of warriors, <strong>refine their stats</strong>, and equip them with powerful gear and talents to build the ultimate squad!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/b506923fa6bff6b7071e1085aa4edf48.poster.avif?t=1773392771\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/b506923fa6bff6b7071e1085aa4edf48.webm?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/b506923fa6bff6b7071e1085aa4edf48.mp4?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Talent System - Massive Customization</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With <strong>260+ unique buff talents</strong> to mix and match, you can:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enhance your heroes' strengths</strong> in different ways</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Boost coin pusher rewards</strong> through strategic synergies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Create explosive combat combos</strong> for maximum farming efficiency</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your perfect setup and <strong>dominate the battlefield!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/c2b027f50f0b2c199f1f095ffa20b28b.poster.avif?t=1773392771\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/c2b027f50f0b2c199f1f095ffa20b28b.webm?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/c2b027f50f0b2c199f1f095ffa20b28b.mp4?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gear Progression & Stat Refinement</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you explore, monsters will drop <strong>100+ powerful equipment pieces</strong> - including rare artifacts with <strong>exclusive special attributes</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progress through the game to:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Refine</strong> your gear's stats</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enhance</strong> their power</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rebuild</strong> them from scratch</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forge your ultimate <strong>endgame equipment</strong> through continuous optimization!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/8f95725012995e61b5ddc23a8727fb38.poster.avif?t=1773392771\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/8f95725012995e61b5ddc23a8727fb38.webm?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/8f95725012995e61b5ddc23a8727fb38.mp4?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tactical Formation & Positioning</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your battle lineup and strategically position heroes to maximize their combat effectiveness!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Freely assemble</strong> your dream team</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Optimize positioning</strong> to enhance skill synergy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adapt formations</strong> for different challenges</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place your warriors where they shine brightest and <strong>dominate the battlefield</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/d94d627fe9de5c03679a8a76a2fb6cb8.poster.avif?t=1773392771\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/d94d627fe9de5c03679a8a76a2fb6cb8.webm?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/d94d627fe9de5c03679a8a76a2fb6cb8.mp4?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Introduction：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Coin Push RPG is a casual idle game incorporating coin-pusher mechanics, featuring abundant content and multiple gameplay modes. The game includes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1:1 Replicated Coin-Pusher Simulator Mode</strong> - Faithfully recreates the arcade coin-pusher experience</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adventure Mode</strong> - Complete with extensive character backgrounds, talent combinations, and equipment selection</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenge Mode</strong> - Combines fast-paced monster battles with idle mechanisms for effortless farming</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will recruit heroes, customize their unique talent skills, assemble various team formations, and lead them on treasure-hunting expeditions. Upgrade your village, craft legendary equipment, and enhance your strength to conquer the Demon King!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/0c250afed965c08fb8d302e1c0a4b7e3.poster.avif?t=1773392771\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/0c250afed965c08fb8d302e1c0a4b7e3.webm?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/0c250afed965c08fb8d302e1c0a4b7e3.mp4?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Coin Push Mode – 1:1 Replica</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game, players can experience an <strong>authentic 1:1 replica of a real coin pusher arcade machine</strong>, featuring:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rotating Wheel (Lucky Spin)</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tower Stacker (Tower Bonus)</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>JP123 Jackpot</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Full-Table Grand Prize</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/bc3f8517f8979228b3251249bb2af113.poster.avif?t=1773392771\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/bc3f8517f8979228b3251249bb2af113.webm?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/bc3f8517f8979228b3251249bb2af113.mp4?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/02bc8e7d9fb022fd5b5a3359268a9a8b.poster.avif?t=1773392771\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/02bc8e7d9fb022fd5b5a3359268a9a8b.webm?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/02bc8e7d9fb022fd5b5a3359268a9a8b.mp4?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Idle Coin Pushing – Relaxing Auto-Battler</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During battles, the coins collected from the <strong>Coin Pusher</strong> will be distributed to your heroes. They’ll only fight for you once they get their fair share!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pay up</strong> to make your heroes work for you—or just <strong>sit back, auto-drop coins</strong>, and let them grind for you effortlessly! <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/1c7aaeb6cbe5654783f02569796e45fb.poster.avif?t=1773392771\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/1c7aaeb6cbe5654783f02569796e45fb.webm?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/1c7aaeb6cbe5654783f02569796e45fb.mp4?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hero Recruitment & Character Development</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every hero comes with <strong>unique backstories and rarity tiers</strong>. Recruit and train a diverse team of warriors, <strong>refine their stats</strong>, and equip them with powerful gear and talents to build the ultimate squad!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/b506923fa6bff6b7071e1085aa4edf48.poster.avif?t=1773392771\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/b506923fa6bff6b7071e1085aa4edf48.webm?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/b506923fa6bff6b7071e1085aa4edf48.mp4?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Talent System - Massive Customization</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With <strong>260+ unique buff talents</strong> to mix and match, you can:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enhance your heroes' strengths</strong> in different ways</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Boost coin pusher rewards</strong> through strategic synergies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Create explosive combat combos</strong> for maximum farming efficiency</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your perfect setup and <strong>dominate the battlefield!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/c2b027f50f0b2c199f1f095ffa20b28b.poster.avif?t=1773392771\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/c2b027f50f0b2c199f1f095ffa20b28b.webm?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/c2b027f50f0b2c199f1f095ffa20b28b.mp4?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gear Progression & Stat Refinement</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you explore, monsters will drop <strong>100+ powerful equipment pieces</strong> - including rare artifacts with <strong>exclusive special attributes</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progress through the game to:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Refine</strong> your gear's stats</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enhance</strong> their power</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rebuild</strong> them from scratch</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forge your ultimate <strong>endgame equipment</strong> through continuous optimization!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/8f95725012995e61b5ddc23a8727fb38.poster.avif?t=1773392771\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/8f95725012995e61b5ddc23a8727fb38.webm?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/8f95725012995e61b5ddc23a8727fb38.mp4?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tactical Formation & Positioning</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your battle lineup and strategically position heroes to maximize their combat effectiveness!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Freely assemble</strong> your dream team</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Optimize positioning</strong> to enhance skill synergy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adapt formations</strong> for different challenges</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place your warriors where they shine brightest and <strong>dominate the battlefield</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/d94d627fe9de5c03679a8a76a2fb6cb8.poster.avif?t=1773392771\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/d94d627fe9de5c03679a8a76a2fb6cb8.webm?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036010/extras/d94d627fe9de5c03679a8a76a2fb6cb8.mp4?t=1773392771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
